description: This common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 50, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 2 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [50 Votes, Common]
